{"article_id":"f6tFkzZvLw7cjEK0","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell failed to garner the support","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"needed to pass the motion","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"to proceed on the watered-down version of the Obamacare repeal bill","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"just after 1:30 a.m. Friday morning .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Three Republicans","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"- Sens . John McCain of Arizona , Lisa Murkowski of Alaska and Susan Collins of Maine -","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"opted to join the 48 Democrats","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"who voted against the measure .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Its failure comes as a devastating blow to McConnell ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"who struggled to get members of his party to come to a consensus on replacement language .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"After months of negotiations , GOP lawmakers were unable to reach an agreement on key provisions ,","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"including how to handle Medicaid cuts in expansion states and whether Planned Parenthood should be defunded .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"The \" skinny repeal \"","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"- which aimed to repeal the aspects of the Affordable Care Act","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"all factions of the conference agreed upon","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"while leaving large portions in tact -","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"was a last-ditch effort by leadership ,","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"who hoped to use the bill as a vehicle","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"to conference with the lower chamber .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Despite McConnell having long been lauded as a legislative wizard ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"his powers of persuasion fell short with the trio of Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"all of whom were vocal about their grievances with the process","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"used to construct the bill .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"It became evident shortly after midnight leadership was struggling to convince hesitant members to get on board .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"While an increasingly-frustrated looking McConnell huddled with Senate Majority Whip John Cornyn on the chamber floor ,","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence partook in a lengthy discussion with McCain","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"in an attempt","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"to coax the Arizona Republican to vote for the measure .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Following its failure ,","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"an emotional McConnell expressed his disappointment","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"GOP lawmakers were unable to deliver on their top campaign promise .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"\" From skyrocketing costs to plummeting choices and collapsing markets , our constituents have suffered through an awful lot under Obamacare .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"We thought","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"they deserved better , \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"he said in his closing remarks on the floor .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"\" It ' s why I , and many of my colleagues , did","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"as we promised","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and voted to repeal this failed law .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"We told our constituents","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"we would vote that way .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"When the moment came ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"most of us did .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"We kept our commitments . \"","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"McCain","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"-","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"who flew in from Arizona","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"after being diagnosed with an aggressive form of brain cancer earlier this week -","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"told reporters","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"\" I thought","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"it was the right vote \"","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"while exiting the Capitol .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"Sen. Bill Cassidy of Louisiana said","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"McCain ' s decision caught him off guard ,","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"telling reporters","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"he ' s frustrated with the outcome ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"but open to taking a bipartisan approach in the future","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"if Democrats are open to working across the aisle .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"\" Obviously I thought","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"he was going to vote yes -","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"I ' ve been working all evening","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"to set up Graham-Cassidy amendment","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"to go onto the conference report , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"\" We thought","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"we had it in a good place , very good place , fantastic place ,","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"so I ' m very disappointed . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":131,"left":108,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":84,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":77,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":73,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":69,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":0,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":70,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":80,"right":82,"relatio